title: Barenaked Ladies - Gordon
description:
I was shocked when I searched for Barenaked Ladies that their first album "Gordon" did not appear!  I knew I found my purpose of the evening.  I dug through the archives and found the original release.  Friend of mine sent it to me from Canada, four months after it&#039;s release, for no certain reason except "Man, you gotta hear these guys!"  I think in later years the album was repackaged in the states with all new cover and liner notes. This is how it originally looked and sounded.

MP3 192Kbps, including cover scans.

Please seed and enjoy!
